creage in the joint development zone jdz between the democratic republic of sao tome  principe and the federal republic of nigeria as well as in the territorial waters of sao tome shareholder administration  erhc energy shareholder administration stock exchange listing erhc energy’s common stock is currently traded on the otc pink marketplace under the symbol “erhe” stock transfer agent shareholder records are maintained by corporate stock transfer “cst” communication concerning the transfer or exchange of shares lost certificates or change of address should be directed to   corporate stock transfer  cherry creek drive south suite  denver co  toll free   tel    fax   email postmastercorporatestockcom website httpwwwcorporatestockcom please contact corporate stock transfer for the further information relating to your ownership of erhc energy inc common stock change of address shareholders should notify cst of change of address by fax and include shareholder name and social security or tax id number  transfer of ownership the following items are required for transfer of freetrading or restricted stock by an individual    original stock certificate    stock power or back of certificate signed with a medallion signature guarantee    letter of instruction    cash or check for  per certificate being issued                                  restricted transfers require company or counsel approval the following items are required for transfer of stock transfer of freetrading or restricted stock by a corporation or partnership    original stock certificate    stock power or back of certificate signed with a medallion signature guarantee    corporate resolution or partnership agreement    letter of instruction    cash or check for  per certificate being issued                                  restricted transfers require company or counsel approval lost stock certificate if a stock certificate is lost stolen or destroyed please notify cst in writing cst will send the necessary forms and instructions for replacing the stock certificate cst will also send an affidavit of loss and an agreement of indemnity both of which must be filled out signed by the registered shareholder and notarized certificates in previous name environmental remediation holding corporation the following items are required for an exchange of certificates original stock certificate transmittal letter or letter of instruction cash or check for  per certificate being issued shareholders do not need to send a medallion signature guarantee unless they are transferring the shares lifting of legend restrictive legends on company stock certificates may be removed if the requirements of rule k of the securities act of   act  are met rule k requires that a period of two years must elapse since the later of the date the stock was acquired from the company or from an affiliate of the company a stock is deemed acquired by a shareholder when he or she pays the full purchase price or other consideration an affiliate generally is an executive officer director or  or more shareholder cst may require at least the following items to remove the restrictive legends from stock certificates    original stock certificate    k letter    documentation fee    fee for each certificate printed if a shareholder is transferring his or her shares to another person or entity then a medallion signature guarantee may be required from his or her broker once a restrictive legend is removed from the certificate it becomes “free trading” your brokerdealer should contact cst to ascertain what items cst requires to remove the restrictive legend from your stock certificate sales of restricted stock restricted stock may be sold in the market if the requirements of rule  of the  act are met a period of one year must have elapsed since the later of the date the stock was acquired from the company or from an affiliate of the company cst may require at least the following items to effect a rule  sale original stock certificate form  broker’s representation letter seller’s representation letter legal opinion of counsel medallion signature guaranteed stock power broker instructions to put stock in street name documentation fee fee for each certificate printed                                  these items are available from a shareholder’s brokerdealer your brokerdealer should contact cst to ascertain what items cst requires to effect a rule  sale  k instruction letter samples       pdf format     word document format  form k shares of k stock are generally restricted from registration until they have been held two years or more in order to remove the restrictive legend after the specified holding period has expired the shareholder should supply proof to cst that heshe is not an affiliate of the company ie officer director  or greater shareholder and provide a copy of form k along with the required company authorization letter to remove the restrictions   the following items are required for legend removal under rule k original stock certificate k letter cash or check for  per certificate being issued and shareholder or broker to remove legend shareholders do not need to send a medallion signature guarantee unless they are transferring the shares   an affiliate is defined as any shareholder of the company that owns  or more of the outstanding shares  k instruction letter samples pdf format  word document format  please note cst will hold such requests for only  days after  days the request will be returned to sender if cst has not received company authorization to remove the legend cst will attempt to get an outside opinion approved by the company or the companys counsel in the the event that the company rejects the outside opinion within  days cst will return the request for legend removal to the presenter with a rejection notice if cst does not receive a company rejection of the outside opinion cst relying on the outside opinion will process the legend removal on the th day if the company or the companys counsel rejects the outside opinion they need to state in writing the reason for the rejection and then cst will return the request for legend removal to the presenter with a copy of the company’s rejection notice forms download form  here   streetholders if your shares are held by your broker please contact your broker directly for information on your account external auditors malone  bailey pc  richmond ave suite  houston tx  tel    fax   wwwmalonebaileycom print   contact us first name last name company phone email comments stock quote newszone erhc energy inc issues april  shareholder update erhc energy inc issues march  shareholder update erhc energy inc signs memorandum of understanding with starcrest energy nigeria limited view more news subscribe to erhc get erhc news updates straight to your news reader with rss signup for the erhc newsletter who we are  oil and gas exploration  offshore drilling who we are erhc energy is a visionary oil and gas company that currently is focused on exploiting its assets  rights to working interests in oil and gas reserves in subsaharan africa in the republic of kenya erhc has a strong alliance with cepsa which is an experienced exploration and production company in  cepsa is scheduled to spud the first well in block a in northwestern kenya the block is in the vicinity of block bb in which significant oil discoveries have recently been announced east africa has emerged in recent years as one of the worlds most exciting new oil provinces in the republic of chad erhc has interests in block bds  which lies next to the doba basin oilfield that field in  had an average daily production of  barrels of crude oil per day  additionally the national petroleum agency of são tomé  príncipe anpstp on behalf of the government of são tomé and principe has awarded erhc  percent working interests in block  of the são tomé  príncipe exclusive economic zone eez erhc also has the option to acquire up to a  percent p