 agreement the jda confirmed the award in  of participating interests “original participating interest” in each of jdz blocks      and  of the jdz during the  licensing round conducted by the jda erhc also jointly bid with internationally recognized technical partners for additional participating interests in the jdz during the  licensing round as a result of the joint bid erhc won additional participating interests “joint bid participating interest” in blocks   and   erhc’s jdz acreage erhc has working interests in six of the nine blocks in the jdz as follows  jdz block   jdz block   jdz block   jdz block   in arbitration jdz block   in arbitration jdz block   the working interest percentages represent erhc’s share of all the hydrocarbon production from the blocks and obligates erhc to pay a corresponding percentage of the costs of drilling production and operating the blocks through exploration phase  in blocks   and  these costs have been carried by the operators the operators can only recover their costs by carrying erhc until production whereupon the operators will recover their costs from production revenues in  sinopec and addax erhcs technical partners and operators in blocks   and  undertook an exploratory drilling campaign across the three blocks that was completed in january  biogenic gas was discovered in each block and discussions continue between the joint development authority and the parties including erhc that hold interests in jdz blocks   and  regarding drilling results the meetings with the jda are aimed at reaching a definitive agreement on how to proceed with the next stage of exploration in the blocks following the expiration of exploration phase i in march   jdz operations update the jdz partnership is currently assessing the data for possible new exploration play concepts in this area more on erhc energys operations   republic of kenya erhc has a production sharing contract psc with the government of the republic of kenya on block a in north